Package org.dmd.dms

Interface Summary
SchemaDefinitionListenerIF The SchemaDefinitionListenerIF should be implemented by objects that are interested in knowing when new definitions have been added to a SchemaManager.
SchemaExtensionIF The SchemaExtensionIF interface should be implemented by classes that extend the basic SchemaManager to provide additional functionality associated with extensions to the basic Meta Schema.
